，記者毛小孟（毛孟靜飾演）受命上陣，堅決提出未被審批的尖銳問題，拍攝被腰斬。另一記者陳家淇（陳安琪飾演）補上，卻又以不屑態度表達對總司令的不信任。錄影完成後，兩名記者因無法履行記者專業職責而相繼請辭，新聞部總監焦明（李怡飾演）一直被受壓力，同樣沒法接受節目成為官方喉舌，卻無奈屈服於客觀現實。電視台老闆包一龍（曹廣榮飾演）下令刪剪全部記者的畫面，只播放總司令的片段，消息轟動整個新聞部，最終新聞部總監在新聞操守與五斗米之間作出決擇。故事彷如寓言，預視香港新聞自由所面臨的壓力<br />\n<a href=\"https://podcast.rthk.hk/podcast/item.php?pid=801&amp;eid=53481&amp;year=2015&amp;lang=en-US\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpodcast.rthk.hk%2Fpodcast%2Fitem.php%3Fpid%3D801%26eid%3D53481%26year%3D2015%26lang%3Den-US&d=SQXEpmicj55cx%2FeODTqnTxR1GjkmqS0yYYF7Sw2QOJY%3D&h=70dd8691\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://podcast.rthk.hk/podcast/item.php?pid=801&amp;eid=53481&amp;year=2015&amp;lang=en-US</a>"},{"pid":"01ebf6b225ceaa9ee071e4e522e072711ab8ca1d","tid":2510374,"uid":78143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T15:46:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmafcEywCtBQJRUfpGJ9wUAL4yE57ZcxJGCnvcXZajbbzp?filename=Kxv7TLe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKxv7TLe.jpg&h=61bcd558&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0801e19aa579568cff9c880eab18400188ae5d5d","tid":2510374,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"30f3fbc207afc6f7a144b077537c688b35985728","tid":2510374,"uid":67338,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T15:40:57.000Z","msg":"10年前RTHK網站未改版<br />\n仲有一堆REAL PLAYER年代既野.畫質差.但係好多80-90年代舊節目<br />\n改版後無哂<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nRTHK改版加有YOUTUBE後無左個舊網站<br />\n唔知同十幾年前將D媒體數碼化有無關係"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T15:46:53.000Z","msg":"到依加windows 仲係唔肯改進內置既player"},{"pid":"4abf16bfe082be3efe2aba85f5652b1bb8c08775","tid":2510374,"uid":13745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T15:47:06.000Z","msg":"講緊我細過三十年前個D甜片戲院既海報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55a0ee7cd38fc0fc8f48ca267b0373c824b975d4","tid":2510374,"uid":28202,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4a3af39a2d6ddeeca5cb2ead1d5840aeb